Package: blouch
Title: BLOUCH: Bayesian Linear Ornstein-Uhlenbeck models for Comparative
    Hypotheses
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mark", "Grabowski", , "mark.walter.grabowski@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7045-9472"))
Description: Bayesian Linear Ornstein-Uhlenbeck models for Comparative
    Hypotheses (BLOUCH) fits adaptive models of continuous trait evolution
    in a Bayesian framework based on categorical or continuous predictors,
    and incorporates measurement error.
